Paper: hep-th/0301243

Date: 2003-01-29

Title: On geometric equations and duality for free higher spins

Authors: Xavier Bekaert and Nicolas Boulanger

Comments: 12 pages, no figure

We provide a general scheme for dualizing higher-spin gauge fields inarbitrary irreducible representations of GL(D,R). We also give a recipe forconstructing Fronsdal-like field equations and Lagrangians for such exoticfields.